\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {\if@rl \I {1.3}\else \textLR {3.1}\fi }{\ignorespaces Three-stage pipeline architecture. Stages communicate via JSONL files on disk, enabling inference to run on any cloud GPU without requiring direct access to local data files.}}{\if@rlmain \I {42}\else \textLR {42}\fi }{figure.caption.2}%
